<p><strong>TAPS 10300 through 10699. Text and Performance.</strong> <em>Experience in dramatic analysis or performance not required. Attendance at first class meeting is mandatory. Each of these courses meets the general education requirement in the arts.</em> Workshops in dramatic technique and attendance at performances at Chicago theaters, in addition to class time, are required.</p>




